overview: As soon as she arrived on the Parisian electro scene in the early 90's, Delphine Palatsi, one of the few women in this field, transformed herself into DJ Sextoy. By imposing a new sound, an innovative style and an uncompromising attitude, she not only revealed her artistic talent but also succeeded in resonating with the creative inspiration of the moment and symbolizing the Paris of an era.
title: Sextoy Stories
